1272
01:18:46.471 --> 01:18:48.097
- Look, please relax, OK?
- I spoke out of turn.

1273
01:18:48.181 --> 01:18:49.807
- Hey. Hey.
- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

1274
01:18:49.850 --> 01:18:51.183
- What are you two bickering about?
- Nothing.

1275
01:18:51.226 --> 01:18:53.477
