1292
01:19:28.889 --> 01:19:31.015
Please tell Chloe
as soon as you get home.

1293
01:19:31.141 --> 01:19:33.893
I just want this situation
to be resolved.

1294
01:19:34.394 --> 01:19:36.228
Do you miss me?

1295
01:19:36.271 --> 01:19:38.272
OK. Bye, bye.

1296
01:19:39.274 --> 01:19:41.525
- Is everything OK?
- Yeah, everything's fine.

1297
01:19:41.610 --> 01:19:43.360
- Are you leaving already?
- Yeah.

1298
01:20:09.930 --> 01:20:12.681
Chris, it's Nola.
Where have I reached you?

1299
01:20:13.141 --> 01:20:14.683
Sardinia.

1300
01:20:14.768 --> 01:20:17.019
I'll be back in five or six days, OK?

1301
01:20:27.697 --> 01:20:29.949
- Good morning, John.
- Oh, you're early, sir.

1302
01:20:30.033 --> 01:20:31.826
- I'll bring the car around.
- Yes.

1303
01:20:38.083 --> 01:20:39.166
