1304
01:20:39.209 --> 01:20:40.793
- Oh, Jesus.
- You lied to me!

1305
01:20:40.836 --> 01:20:42.336
- Quiet!
- I wanna see Chloe!

1306
01:20:42.462 --> 01:20:44.213
- Quiet, quiet.
- I wanna talk to Chloe.

1307
01:20:44.297 --> 01:20:45.214
Look, Christ, Christ.

1308
01:20:45.340 --> 01:20:46.549
No, no, no, listen.
Listen, I can explain.

1309
01:20:46.591 --> 01:20:47.842
I wanna talk to Chloe.
You're a liar! You're a liar!

1310
01:20:47.926 --> 01:20:49.093
I can explain. I... Taxi!

1311
01:20:49.094 --> 01:20:50.469
- I'm not going anywhere with you.
- Taxi!

1312
01:20:50.554 --> 01:20:52.805
- I'm not going anywhere with you.
- Calm down.

1313
01:20:52.848 --> 01:20:55.683
- Nola! Nola, calm down. Calm down.
- You're a liar! You're a liar!

1314
01:20:55.725 --> 01:20:57.226
I came home deliberately,
I came home early.

1315
01:20:57.310 --> 01:20:59.812
You're a liar! I wanna talk to Chloe.

1316
01:20:59.855 --> 01:21:02.481
- I wanna talk to Chloe!
- Calm down. Calm the fuck down!

1317
01:21:02.566 --> 01:21:06.443
I wanna talk to Chloe.
You liar! You're a liar!

1318
01:21:06.987 --> 01:21:08.362
You're a liar!

1319
01:21:12.325 --> 01:21:15.244
I decided to cut the trip short
because all this is eating away at me.

1320
01:21:15.370 --> 01:21:17.121
I only came back
the day before yesterday

1321
01:21:17.247 --> 01:21:19.373
because I need a week
in the city to deal with Chloe

1322
01:21:19.499 --> 01:21:22.334
- without you breathing down my neck.
- You're driving me crazy!

1323
01:21:22.377 --> 01:21:24.336
I don't know whether
to believe you or not.

1324
01:21:24.379 --> 01:21:26.130
- Please believe me, Nola.
- Well, did you tell her?

1325
01:21:26.256 --> 01:21:27.590
I was about to when you called.

1326
01:21:27.632 --> 01:21:28.716
What does that have to do with anything?

1327
01:21:28.758 --> 01:21:29.967
- I got flustered.
- Oh, please!

1328
01:21:30.010 --> 01:21:31.510
