telling you that I'm still in Greece.

1330
01:21:33.722 --> 01:21:36.390
- You said Sardinia.
- I... I was talking fast.

1331
01:21:36.474 --> 01:21:38.893
I... I didn't want her to know
what I was talking about.

1332
01:21:38.977 --> 01:21:40.519
Well, she has to know eventually.

1333
01:21:40.896 --> 01:21:42.855
- I can't tell her.
- Then I will.

1334
01:21:42.898 --> 01:21:43.898
Nola, stop!

1335
01:21:44.024 --> 01:21:46.275
Well, this is crazy.
We're having a child together!

1336
01:21:46.359 --> 01:21:47.902
We don't have to have a child together.

1337
01:21:47.986 --> 01:21:49.737
It would make life
a hell of a lot simpler if we didn't.

1338
01:21:49.779 --> 01:21:51.864
Yeah, simpler for you, but not for me.

1339
01:21:52.908 --> 01:21:55.159
It occurred to me
that even if you had the child,

