01:22:06.671 --> 01:22:09.298
If I don't do what you say,
you're gonna go to my wife.

1346
01:22:09.674 --> 01:22:11.258
Were you lying to me?

1347
01:22:11.384 --> 01:22:12.801
All those times we made love,

1348
01:22:12.886 --> 01:22:15.888
