1373
01:25:48.393 --> 01:25:51.520
I wish had someone to confide in,
but it's all so damn secretive.

1374
01:25:51.604 --> 01:25:54.022
Look, Chris,
if I don't do something about this,

1375
01:25:54.107 --> 01:25:56.150
