1379
01:26:04.659 --> 01:26:06.285
Nola, tomorrow is fine.

1380
01:26:06.411 --> 01:26:10.622
- What time will you get back from work?
- Same time I always get off, 6:30.

1381
01:26:10.665 --> 01:26:12.166
So you'll be home by a quarter to seven?

1382
01:26:12.292 --> 01:26:15.794
Yeah. Chris, you make me say
these things. I hate myself for them.

1383
01:26:15.920 --> 01:26:18.046
- I just want us to be together.
- We will be.

1384
01:26:20.049 --> 01:26:22.551
You were very nervy
all through the ballet.

1385
01:26:22.635 --> 01:26:23.802
