1411
01:27:28.826 --> 01:27:30.994
- What for?
- The Woman in White.

1412
01:27:31.120 --> 01:27:33.956
- I heard it's great.
- I thought you hated musicals.

1413
01:27:33.998 --> 01:27:35.707
No, that's not so.

1414
01:27:35.750 --> 01:27:39.253
- And anyway, you love his music.
- Well, that's great.

1415
01:27:39.337 --> 01:27:41.255
I'll have to meet you
outside the theater,

1416
01:27:41.339 --> 01:27:43.715
'cause I'll be coming
straight from the gallery.

1417
01:27:43.758 --> 01:27:45.509
Why don't you take the chauffeur?

1418
01:27:45.510 --> 01:27:49.137
I'll grab a taxi, and with any luck
I can get an hour of tennis in.

1419
01:27:50.098 --> 01:27:52.224
You're so sweet.

1420
01:27:52.267 --> 01:27:54.768
You knew how much
I wanted to see that.

1421
01:27:57.772 --> 01:28:00.607
All right, come to bed,
because you're tired, my darling.

1422
01:28:00.650 --> 01:28:02.484
OK, I will.

1423
01:28:05.405 --> 01:28:08.115
- Hello?
- Hello, Nola?

1424
01:28:09.409 --> 01:28:11.660
When you get off work today,
